"99:6:2" : {s: 99, a: 6, w: 2, r: "صدر", t: "يَصْدُرُ", l: "يَصْدُرُ", lc: 1, tl: "yaṣduru", lb: "প্রকাশ হওয়া",e: "will proceed", b: "বেরিয়ে আসবে", i: "keluar", f: 1, rm: "To return from, come back, proceed, issue or emanate from, go forward, advance or promote, come to pass, happen, emanate from, strike on the chest/breast, commence. Anything that fronts, or faces one; hence breast, chest or bosom [often meaning his mind]. The fore part of anything. Going, or turning back and away.", ag: "فعل مضارع ", eg: "Verb Imperfect ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPF", qual: "", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "يَصْدُرُ"},
